data.title: Adam DeVine
data.meta_description: Adam Patrick DeVine is an American comedian, actor, producer and screenwriter. He is one of the stars and co-creators of the Comedy Central comedy television series Workaholics and Adam DeVine's House Party.
data.text:
For the Scottish association football player, see Adam Devine (footballer).

Not to be confused with Adam Levine.

Adam Patrick DeVine (born November 7, 1983) is an American comedian, actor, producer and screenwriter. He is one of the stars and co-creators of the Comedy Central comedy television series Workaholics[1] and Adam DeVine's House Party.[2]
